# Coding

- Server Components default; `"use client"` only for state/effects/events
- `await params` / `await searchParams` (Promises in Next 16)
- `type` for props; strict TS; no `any`
- `<Link>` / `<Image>` — except LCP hero (`HeroSection` + `LcpImagePreload`)
- `pageMetadata()` for all `generateMetadata`; `[...slug]` → `join('/')`
- GROQ only in `sanity/lib/queries.ts` via `safeFetch`
- No Sanity/nodemailer in client components
- Tailwind v4: `dq-*`, `ms/me`, `bg-black/50`, no CSS-in-JS

# Naming protocol

## Files
- Components: `PascalCase.tsx`; default export matches filename
- `lib/`, `sanity/lib/`: `camelCase.ts`
- App routes: kebab-case segments; route-private UI in `app/**/_components/`
- Next.js special files: `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `route.ts`, `error.tsx`

## TypeScript
- Props: `type ComponentNameProps = { ... }` — never bare `Props`
- Domain types: `type` in `lib/types/`; PascalCase nouns
- Prefer `type` over `interface`; reuse shared types (`NavNode`, not local duplicates)
- No `any`; use `unknown` + narrowing

## Functions
- `get*` — cached Sanity fetchers (`sanity/lib/fetchers.ts`)
- `safeFetch` — low-level GROQ with null fallback
- `fetch*` — multi-source page orchestration (e.g. `fetchCmsPage`)
- `resolve*` — SEO/path fallbacks; `build*` — JSON-LD, nav trees
- `handle*` — client event handlers only

## GROQ (`queries.ts`)
- Private fragments: `SCREAMING_SNAKE`
- Exports: `camelCase` + `Query` suffix (`postsQuery`, `courseBySlugDeepQuery`)

## Constants
- `SCREAMING_SNAKE` for module config (`PAGE_SLUG`, `SITE_URL`)
- Reuse `SITE_URL` from `lib/seo` — do not duplicate

## Abbreviations (allowlist)
- OK when domain-clear: `dq`, `cms`, `og`, `llm`, `nav`, `faq`, `seo`
- Spell out opaque names: `homepageSettings`, not `hp`

## CSS
- Tailwind utilities first; brand via `dq-*`
- Custom globals: kebab-case (`.skip-link`); Reveal uses `.rv-*`
